Supply chain attack - attacker infects one of many process in chain therefore have an impact on final effect. 
For example attacker can infect a software which is then delivered to castomers. Customers trust their suppliers and download infected software.

There are many steps before technology comes to us. Infectiong one in most cases infects entier chain.

To prevent it you can should use small supplier base. Make sure that suppliers have proper security in place.